PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Tykeith L. TURNER, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 158068
COA: 336406 Supreme Court of Michigan. April 25, 2019

Order

On order of the Chief Justice, the motion of defendant-appellant to extend the time for filing his brief is GRANTED. The brief will be accepted as timely filed if submitted on or before July 12, 2019.
